How to create an issue

Okay, something has gone wrong, you’ve worked through the trouble-shooting tips, and you’ve come to the conclusion that there is a problem with the code.

  • Go to the PyMyoVent respository

  • Click on the Issues tab

  • Click on the Green “New issue” button
